00:13:20.346 --> 00:13:24.058
great art museums in the world
and you say, "Yeah,

00:13:24.058 --> 00:13:28.489
I've seen these Picassos.
I've seen these Rembrandts

00:13:28.489 --> 00:13:31.029
before.
