afresh.

00:13:42.539 --> 00:13:43.950
Well, what's the solution to
that?

00:13:43.950 --> 00:13:49.229
The solution to that might be a
kind of amnesia,

00:13:49.229 --> 00:13:53.610
a kind of progressive lack of
memory.

00:13:53.610 --> 00:13:55.947
So here I am,
100 years, 1,000 years,

00:13:55.947 --> 00:13:58.740
around 500,000 years,
whatever it may be.

00:13:58.740 --> 00:14:00.470
You're getting pretty bored
